thread.title: Kevin
thread.title_full: Extra Space Storage reviewed by Kevin

author: Kevin
title: Kevin
text:
The folks there were extremely courteous and helpful through the startup process, and the units are clean and secure from what I can tell.
My only gripe is that you are not signing a contract at a particular rate. Once you move all your stuff in, the price can go up and does.
